&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Join Us in Revolutionizing Oncology Care!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At &lt;strong&gt;Canopy&lt;/strong&gt;, we’re transforming healthcare for cancer patients by shifting from episodic treatment to continuous, patient-centered care. Our cutting-edge technology empowers patients to manage symptoms and access support anytime, anywhere—ensuring they never feel alone. With &lt;strong&gt;Canopy, the clinic is always with them&lt;/strong&gt;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our innovative approach not only enhances the patient experience but also aligns clinic revenue with better health outcomes, creating a true win-win for everyone involved. By driving a 20% increase in treatment adherence and strengthening patient-provider connections, Canopy delivers life-saving results while elevating patient satisfaction to new heights.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Join us in shaping the future of oncology care! 🌿&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Your Mission&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;As a &lt;strong&gt;Backend Tech Lead&lt;/strong&gt;, you’ll take ownership of Canopy’s backend architecture, ensuring the performance, scalability, and reliability of our platform. You’ll work closely with a talented team of engineers and stakeholders to design and implement high-quality, secure, and resilient backend systems that power our healthcare solutions. By providing both technical vision and hands-on expertise, you will help drive Canopy’s ability to scale effectively, enabling us to deliver innovative oncology care solutions that make a real difference.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Lead Backend Strategy&lt;/strong&gt; – Architect scalable backend systems to support our growing platform.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Optimize Performance&lt;/strong&gt; – Design efficient and resilient services that handle high data volumes in real time.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ensure Code Quality&lt;/strong&gt; – Enforce best practices for development, testing, and deployment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Mentor &amp;amp; Guide&lt;/strong&gt; – Support engineers at various experience levels through technical mentorship and knowledge-sharing.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Stay Ahead of Trends&lt;/strong&gt; – Keep up with emerging technologies and leverage them to enhance our backend ecosystem.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Bring&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;8+ years of engineering &amp;amp; architecture experience in enterprise software.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Expertise in backend development (5+ years, preferably JavaScript/TypeScript, NodeJS).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven experience designing scalable, performant technical platforms.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with cloud services (AWS/GCP) and database optimization.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong leadership, collaboration, and communication skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bonus Points&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in regulated industries such as healthcare or fintech.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven ability to lead and mentor engineering teams in high-growth environments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A track record of delivering complex, high-impact technical projects.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
