&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Your Mission&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;As a &lt;strong&gt;Senior Product Manager&lt;/strong&gt; at Canopy, you will own the strategy and execution of a large component of Canopy’s platform. You will work closely with our users to build empathy for the healthcare professionals and patients who rely on Canopy’s platform and use those insights to develop best-in-class software solutions to their most pressing problems. You will join an extraordinary team of individuals who are as driven as you are to change the face of cancer care and improve the lives of patients. Your work will directly influence how care teams engage with patients, optimize workflows, and deliver life-changing outcomes.&lt;/p&gt;
